{"tid":2353742,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【沉冤待雪】鑑證科警員承認未於防煙門套指模 指現場未發現任何指摸","createTime":"2021-01-05T03:41:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T04:01:11.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7eb1d9dddb809e33985c9b447d46c10a8650340b","tid":2353742,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T03:41:02.000Z","msg":"【沉冤待雪】鑑證科警員承認未於防煙門套指模 指現場未發現任何指摸<br />\nJanuary 4, 2021<br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n周梓樂死因研訊接近尾聲，第25日亦傳召了兩名鑑證科警員，分別為高級警員袁志雄和督察賴振文。警員在代表家屬的鄭大律師追問下，承認未有關注3樓的防煙門，未有於門上掃取指模；又指在現場未發現任何指摸。另外今日所有死因庭證供已經完成，明日起將會進入結案陳詞的皆段。<br />\n<br />\n詳細報導內容: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3rPv5Zn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3rPv5Zn&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuObnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=5bd1b94f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3rPv5Zn</a>"},{"pid":"707c0e40ac004196f84f5d5186d7c8c8bb021ab5","tid":2353742,"uid":34869,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T03:43:50.000Z","msg":"之前仲想屈周梓樂自己爬出<br />\n又冇指模又冇腳印, 凌空飛過去咩屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f19a977d1759402f6220702963db5b46f4d4f754","tid":2353742,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T03:47:48.000Z","msg":"黑警殺人，全家不得好死"},{"pid":"9e1838817ae017170382d5437842a1c740945127","tid":2353742,"uid":33263,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T03:50:43.000Z","msg":"簡單講 即係差佬掟人落樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />殺人犯"},{"pid":"3a63cb9be2761d410e70a28cb5e8a6833bf0e424","tid":2353742,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T03:58:14.000Z","msg":"公職人員行為失當"},{"pid":"2c9897cb906598889a562292ab709425173e38d8","tid":2353742,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T04:01:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkg